channel.title: Need Help!
channel.description:
Guys, I really need a coder. [Why Do I need a coder [STORY]]: My computer was owned 6+ months ago, and I were waiting to repair it, had no time, cause I was really busy. Now I got it back, but got huge java problems, so I need someones help, cause my friend really need server, and I need coder :P I could do everything myself, but cause of those problems, I'm in need to ask you guys for help. Please, some kind of you, e-mail me (mod-vlad-@hotmail.com) if you can help me, and I will answer, and we will deal. [NB!] I can't pay real life money.
For a future,- - Thanks.
